ala.com/raghuleela-mega-mall-mumbai}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Korum Mall]]\n| [[Thane]]\n| 2009\n| {{convert|450000|sqft|m2|abbr=on}}\n| <ref>{{cite web|title=Korum Mall|url=http://www.korum.in/}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Growel's 101]]\n| [[Kandivali]], [[Mumbai]]\n| 2010\n| {{convert|750000|sqft|m2|abbr=on}}\n| <ref name=\"Growel's 101 Inauguration\"/><ref name='Mall Mania'/><ref name=\"Growel's 101\"/>\n|-\n| [[R-Mall]]\n| [[Mulund]], [[Mumbai]]\n| 2003\n| {{convert|250000|sqft|m2|abbr=on}}\n| <ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rmall.in/index1.html |title=R Mall |publisher=Runwal Group |accessdate=26 April 2010 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100415124344/http://www.rmall.in/index1.html |archivedate=15 April 2010 |df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Crossroads Mall (Mumbai)]]\n| [[Worli]], [[Mumbai]]\n| 1999\n| {{convert|150000|sqft|m2|abbr=on}}\n| <ref>{{cite web |url=http://mumbai.dialindia.com/crossroads-mall-14765.html |title=Crossroads Mall &#124; Mumbai |publisher=Mumbai.dialindia.com |accessdate=6 November 2012 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121218091408/http://mumbai.dialindia.com/crossroads-mall-14765.html |archive-date=18 December 2012 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n|-\n| Fountain Square\n| [[Kharghar]]\n| 2008\n|\n|\n|-\n| [[R City Mall]]\n| [[Ghatkopar]], [[Mumbai]]\n| 2009\n| {{convert|1200000|sqft|m2|abbr=on}}\n| <ref name=\"The city has it all\" />\n|-\n| [[Neptune Magnet Mall]]\n| [[Bhandup]], [[Mumbai]]\n| 2011\n| {{convert|1056000|sqft|m2|abbr=on}}\n| <ref>{{cite web|title=Neptune Magnet Mall|url=https://mumbai.mallsmarket.com/malls/neptune-magnet-mall-bhandup-west}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Neptune Magnet Mall Failure|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/mumbai/mumbai-mega-mall-fails-turned-into-offices/articleshow/58057231.cms}}</ref>\n|-\n| City Centre, Nashik\n| Untwadi, [[Nashik]]\n| 2009\n| {{convert|900000|sqft|m2|abbr=on}}\n| <ref name='City Centre Nashik'/><ref name='City Centre Nashik Information'/><ref name='City Centre