-north/cid/1279243}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Star Mall Information|url=https://www.unimarkgroup.com/project/star-mall.php}}</ref>\n|-\n| AMP Baishakhi (Vaishaakkhi) Mall\n| Sector-2, [[Salt Lake City, Kolkata]]\n| 2014\n| {{convert|202150|sqft|m2|abbr=on}}\n| <ref>{{cite web|title=Salt Lake (AMP Mall) Information|url=http://innateindia.com/project-inner.php?pro_id=14}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=New Mall In Salt Lake (AMP Mall)|url=https://www.m.indiablooms.com/finance-details/45/amp-vaisaakkhi-mall-to-be-unveiled-in-kolkata.html}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Forum (Kolkata)|Forum Mall (Forum Courtyard)]]\n| Elgin Road, [[Bhawanipore]], [[Kolkata]]\n| 2003\n| {{convert|200000|sqft|m2|abbr=on}}\n| <ref>{{cite web|title=Forum Mall|url=https://kolkata.mallsmarket.com/malls/forum-mall-elgin-road}}</ref>\n|-\n| Metropolis Mall, Kolkata\n| [[Hiland Park, Kolkata|Hiland Park]], [[Kolkata]]\n| 2004\n| {{convert|175000|sqft|m2|abbr=on}}\n| <ref>{{cite web|title=Hiland Park Metropolis Mall|url=https://kolkata.mallsmarket.com/malls/metropolis-mall-hiland-park}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Hiland Park Metropolis Mall is about to open|url=https://m.telegraphindia.com/states/west-bengal/mall-with-class-for-the-mass-convenience-and-price-usp-of-retail-food-entertainment-centre/cid/1084438}}</ref>\n|-\n| Sentrum Mall, Krishnanagar\n| [[Krishnanagar, Nadia|Krishnanagar]]\n| 2015\n| {{convert|150000|sqft|m2|abbr=on}}\n| <ref>{{cite web|title=Krishnanagar Sentrum Mall|url=https://www.shristicorp.com/property/sentrum-krishnagar/}}</ref>\n|-\n| Downtown Mall, Salt Lake\n| Sector-3, [[Salt Lake City, Kolkata]]\n| 2009\n| {{convert|120000|sqft|m2|abbr=on}}\n| <ref>{{cite web|title=Salt Lake Downtown Mall|url=https://m.timesofindia.com/city/kolkata/Salt-Lake-to-get-two-new-malls/articleshow/4210031.cms}}</ref>\n|-\n| Wood Square Mall\n| [[Narendrapur|Narendrapur, Kolkata]]\n| 2015\n| {{convert|120000|sqft|m2|abbr=on}}\n| <ref>{{cite web|title=Wood Square Mall|url=https://www.unimarkgroup.com/project/